headline: Two Reasons to Watch ALLE and One to Stay Cautious
summary: Allegion has followed the market’s trajectory closely, rising in tandem with the S&P 500 over the past six months. The stock has climbed by 17.4% to $141.41 per share while the index has gained 13%.
